.TH CONV-SHELL 1 "July 2026" "ConVigurator Manual"
.SH NAME
conv-shell \- configuration manager for Fish shell and Starship prompt.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B conv-shell
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B conv-shell
installs clean, optimized profiles for the Fish shell and the Starship prompt on the system.
It synchronizes configurations across root and standard user directories.
It implements the __starship_auto_tune auto-tuning system to prevent terminal hangs due to command execution timeouts.
.SH SEE ALSO
conv-warden(1), conv-alias(1)
